          <td style=3D"padding-bottom: 36px; color: #000000; font-size: 16p=
x; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">It=E2=80=99s also a=
 practical choice: Blazy is only 40, and yet already has the technical expe=
rtise to fully leverage Chanel=E2=80=99s exceptional metiers and atelier. H=
e=E2=80=99ll make it about the clothes and, in turn, hopefully, elicit desi=
re. For years, people have lamented the end of the star-designer era, and i=
n some ways, this appointment represents the actual end. Blazy is a true ta=
lent, but the brand is the star. If his Chanel works, it will force every o=
ther major house to rethink their configuration and creative leadership. <b=
r/><br/>Trotter=E2=80=99s arrival at Bottega is also practical, if perhaps =
not <i>as</i> inspired. Kering could have gone a million different ways, bu=
t they chose someone=E2=80=94a woman and a <i>mother</i>, mind you=E2=80=94=
who has spent decades preparing for this position. She=E2=80=99s a grownup,=
 and will likely create some continuity for the folks at
Bottega Veneta, who are certainly sad to see Blazy depart. <br/></td>
